WolfBlade::

She looked at him as if he was insane. "Uh, What? No, this is Urthe, 
in the year 9037 AGW.  You know, After the Great War? Prehistoric my 
tail end." she said with a chuckle. "Prehistoric, oh that's a good 
one. No one in the Matrix Sliders would have made a miscalulation 
such as to send me to anther dimention...." She stopped and the look 
of shock on her face. "Oh my Matrix. No wonder you didn't know me or 
what I was talking about."  She looked at 
Windlord. "Prehistoric........earth?"
